1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,500
A personal knowledge base fails when unverified claims quietly become facts.

2
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:14,000
Fact Atlas adapts to desktop and mobile, connecting active exploration and daily discovery in three tabs.

3
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Relay accepts text, a public link, or a screenshot for deep verification.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:30,500
Signals routes global news by topic and date, one swipeable card at a time.

5
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:38,500
Gonka ranks importance and keeps a receipt; importance is never presented as truth.

6
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:46,500
A selected signal then enters FactRelay evidence retrieval and cross-checking.

7
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:55,000
Every source keeps its publisher, date, URL, stance, and reliability.

8
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:03,000
Truth Score is calculated by deterministic code, not generated by a model.

9
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:11,500
Invalid source indexes are rejected, and model disagreement stays visible.

10
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:19,500
The FactRelay supervisor coordinates six bounded subagents and reusable Skills.

11
00:01:19,500 --> 00:01:28,000
Kimi-K2.6 forms the first evidence-based investigation.

12
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:36,500
MiniMax-M2.7 challenges circular reporting, chronology, and missing context.

13
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:45,000
Every inference preserves its upstream Gonka Request ID and order.

14
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:53,000
All inference uses GonkaRouter; a receipt proves provenance, not truth.

15
00:01:53,000 --> 00:02:01,000
The user decides what enters the Atlas and confirms the place candidate.

16
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:11,000
A dark Mapbox globe makes bright fact nodes and explainable links visible.

17
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Knowledge without a reliable place remains unplaced; coordinates are never invented.

18
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:25,000
The evidence snapshot stays browser-local as a private knowledge lineage.

19
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:30,000
Fact Atlas. Build a knowledge world. Every fact keeps receipts.
